name: SIDNEYLE Signature Brush Set
description:
This 8 piece Basic Must-Have Backstage Brush Set comes with:
RETAILS FOR $235!!! 
*Large Flat Paddle Foundation Brush
*Duo Fiber Brush
*Contouring Brush
*Sable Shader Eye Shadow Brush
*Deluxe Pointed Crease Blending Brush
*Duo Sided Mini Fluff & Pointed Crease Brush
*Duo Sided Mini Smudger & Oval Brush
*Sable Angle Liner Brush

name: Large Deluxe Flat Foundation Brush
description: Synthetic Flat Paddle brush used for creamy or liquid products.  The sleek edges helps with harder to reach areas on the face.

name: Duo Fiber Face Brush
description: Rounded synthetic and soft natural face brush used for creamy emollient or liquid products.  Can be used to dust on light powder.  This brush helps gives foundation an "airbrush" effect.

name: Angle Contour Brush
description: Super soft slightly angled natural brush used for contouring and highlighting the face.  Can be used for blending powder products.  Great for blush.

name: Deluxe Pointed Crease Blending Brush
description: A soft natural blending brush, primarily used on the crease around the eyes.  Provides a nice airbrush blend.

name: Sable Shader Eye Shadow Brush
description: Dense Sable brush used for applying eye shadows or powder products.  The Sable hair on brush helps pick up and pack on products.  Use the super round edges to define hard lines.

name: Duo Sided Mini Smudger and Oval Brush
description: Soft natural mini eye smudger on one side(or it may be used as a lip brush).  Oval fluff blending brush on the other side.

name: Duo Sided Mini Fluff/Pointed Crease Shader
description: Soft natural mini blend brush on one side for blending compact areas and mini shader brush on the other side.

name: Sable Angle Liner
description: Sable flat firmed angle liner brush.  It can be used with creamy emollient/powder products on the eyes, or for the eyebrows.

name: LUS Glue
description:
*False Eyelash glue
*Used for double Eye Lid

The best glue I've used so far. Made in Korea. Comes with easy applicator wand.  Dries fast and stay flexible on lashes.  These glue are more durable than DUO and Ardell's glue IMO.  I've been a makeup artist for over 12 years and have worked with MAC Cosmetics....i absolutely LOVE these glue. 

**SUNKU glue changed their name to LUS...same exact formula...
